729150f-a.title: Richmond: Midland Avenue - Grimsby Street
729150f-a.text:
Midland Avenue, east side, south from Grimsby to Freeborn Streets. The two-story building, on the right, is occupied by the United Civic League of Midland Beach, lInc.
Augmumt, 19, 1935
P.L. Sperr

art of the same, as seen from Freeborn Street.
August 19, 1935.
